text: Merethe Jensen (born 2 April 1970) is a Danish equestrian. She competed in the individual jumping event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Danish female equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Denmark Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:People from Roskilde
